description: Haitong ETF Series - Haitong CSI300 Index ETF is an exchange traded fund launched and managed by Hai Tong Asset Management (HK) Limited. . The fund invests in the public equity markets of China. It seeks to invest in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in the stocks of companies of large-cap companies. It seeks to replicate the performance of the CSI 300 Index, by investing in the stocks of companies as per their weightings in the index. Haitong ETF Series - Haitong CSI300 Index ETF was formed on March 5, 2014 and is domiciled in Hong Kong.
name: Haitong CSI300 Index ETF
